    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 的收益将考验标准普尔 500 指数 4 万亿美元的复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/nvidia-s-earnings-will-test-the-s-p-500-s-4-trillion-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 ChatGPT 推出以来的大约两年时间里，英伟达公司股价上涨了近 3 万亿美元，几乎改变了美国股市，使这家人工智能芯片制造巨头对一系列股票指数产生了巨大影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/nvidia-s-earnings-will-test-the-s-p-500-s-4-trillion-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:32:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强、英伟达前景不乐观 新兴市场受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/strong-dollar-nvidia-suspense-keep-emerging-markets-in-check</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美元近期的抛售幅度过大，大多数新兴市场货币周三均出现下跌。股票投资者等待当天晚些时候 Nvidia Inc. 的业绩来判断科技行业的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/strong-dollar-nvidia-suspense-keep-emerging-markets-in-check</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:31:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着拘留时间临近，法国正在考虑对 Telegram 首席执行官采取下一步行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/telegram-ceo-to-face-off-with-judge-when-four-day-detention-ends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[接下来的 24 小时将决定 Telegram 首席执行官帕维尔·杜罗夫 (Pavel Durov) 的命运，他因被控允许犯罪分子不受限制地使用该消息应用程序而在巴黎被拘留了四天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/telegram-ceo-to-face-off-with-judge-when-four-day-detention-ends</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:29:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国敦促 Telegram 严厉打击 Deepfake 性犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/south-korea-urges-telegram-to-crack-down-on-deepfake-sex-crimes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于此类内容激增，韩国政府已要求通讯应用程序 Telegram 和其他社交媒体公司从其平台上删除露骨的深度伪造性爱图片。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/south-korea-urges-telegram-to-crack-down-on-deepfake-sex-crimes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 09:54:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美团销售额攀升，外卖业务在低迷时期蓬勃发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/meituan-s-sales-beat-estimates-on-strong-food-delivery-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美团外卖主营业务扩张速度快于预期，其季度业绩超出预期，这对越来越担心国内消费疲软的投资者来说是一个积极信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/meituan-s-sales-beat-estimates-on-strong-food-delivery-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 08:45:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据盗窃激增，德国企业成本达到 2670 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/german-firms-costs-hit-267-billion-in-year-as-data-theft-soars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据科技游说团体 Bitkom 的一项调查，过去一年，超过 80% 的德国公司成为数据盗窃、工业间谍或破坏的受害者，造成的累计损失增加近三分之一，达到创纪录的 2670 亿欧元（2980 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/german-firms-costs-hit-267-billion-in-year-as-data-theft-soars</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乐高 CEO 希望通过更多游戏交易复制《堡垒之夜》的成功</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/lego-ceo-wants-to-copy-fortnite-success-with-more-game-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乐高首席执行官表示，乐高公司与 Epic Games 合作推出的《堡垒之夜》大获成功，自推出以来已覆盖 8300 万人，该公司目前正在寻求新的数字合作伙伴关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/lego-ceo-wants-to-copy-fortnite-success-with-more-game-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆克什·安巴尼预计将在年度股东大会上提供有关 Reliance Jio 和零售业 IPO 的详细信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/ambani-s-reliance-agm-may-offer-clues-on-reliance-jio-reliance-retail-ipos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当亚洲首富穆克什·安巴尼 (Mukesh Ambani) 于周四发表备受期待的年度公开演讲时，信实工业有限公司 (Reliance Industries Ltd.) 的股东们将会仔细分析他的讲话，以了解其电信和零售巨头上市的具体细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/ambani-s-reliance-agm-may-offer-clues-on-reliance-jio-reliance-retail-ipos</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 04:34:32 GMT</pubDate>
